---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: How Martinez & Associates Increased Case Value to $127K Monthly" description="A Toronto personal injury firm transformed lead response and referral systems.">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/legal-services/personal-injury" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Personal Injury Law
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Case Study</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">5 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          How Martinez & Associates Increased Monthly Case Value to $127K
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          A Toronto personal injury firm transformed lead response and referral systems.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">92%</div>
              <div class="text-red-100">Lead Response Rate</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">47%</div>
              <div class="text-red-100">Intake Conversion</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">3.6x</div>
              <div class="text-red-100">Referral Increase</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">$127K</div>
              <div class="text-red-100">Monthly Case Value</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

          <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl my-8 not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Client Overview</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Firm:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Martinez & Associates</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Location:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Toronto, ON</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Practice:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Personal injury</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Focus:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">MVA, slip & fall, medical malpractice</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>

          <p>
            Jennifer Martinez had skilled lawyers but inconsistent case flow. Leads called and didn't get quick responses. Clients felt ignored during long cases. Referrals happened randomly. Good cases were going to competitors.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Solution</h2>

          <p>We implemented instant lead response with 24/7 availability, automated case qualification, milestone-based client updates, systematic review requests at settlement, and structured referral campaigns to past clients.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Results</h2>

          <p>Lead response rate hit 92%. Intake conversion jumped to 47%. Referrals increased 3.6x. Monthly case value grew to $127K. Better cases, faster signing, happier clients.</p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-red-500 pl-6 my-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-4">
              "The instant response changed everything. We were losing cases to firms who answered faster. Now we're first, every time."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 not-italic">â€” Jennifer Martinez, Partner</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-orange-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your PI Practice?</h3>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-red-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
